import React from "react";
import { TableRow, TableCell, IconButton, Tooltip,Link } from "@material-ui/core";
import { VisibilitySharp, EditSharp, DeleteSharp } from '@material-ui/icons';

const TableList = ({ id, firstname, lastname, email }) => {
    return (
        <>
            <TableRow>
                <TableCell>{id}</TableCell>
                <TableCell>{firstname} {lastname}</TableCell>
                <TableCell>{email}</TableCell>
                <TableCell>
                    <Tooltip title='view' arrow>
                        <IconButton size="small">
                            <Link href='/'>
                                <VisibilitySharp color='primary' />
                            </Link>
                        </IconButton>
                    </Tooltip>
                    <Tooltip title='Edit' arrow>

                        <IconButton size="small">
                            <EditSharp />
                        </IconButton>
                    </Tooltip>

                    <Tooltip title='Delete' arrow>
                        <IconButton size="small">
                            <DeleteSharp color='error' />
                        </IconButton>
                    </Tooltip>

                </TableCell>
            </TableRow>
        </>
    );
};

export default TableList;
